303
00:16:31,458 --> 00:16:37,083
Whooooaa! AAAAHH!

304
00:16:38,583 --> 00:16:39,666
Yes!

305
00:16:40,541 --> 00:16:42,750
Keiichi, it's you...

306
00:16:42,833 --> 00:16:46,083
Man, she really takes
