326
00:17:55,041 --> 00:17:58,250
I gues I was just a little
surprised, that's all.

327
00:17:58,333 --> 00:18:00,375
It was some kind
of practice, wasn't it?

328
00:18:00,458 --> 00:18:03,458
Well... I guess
you could say that.

329
00:18:04,083 --> 00:18:07,250
I have to admint that I was
a little jealous though.

330
00:18:07,333 --> 00:18:10,875
