354
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:24,375
I didn't do anything except say
"I love you."

355
00:19:26,583 --> 00:19:31,625
I love you. I love you. I love
you. I love you. I love you.

356
00:19:31,708 --> 00:19:33,208
Whoa whoa whoa!!

357
00:19:33,291 --> 00:19:35,625
