two are behind this.

364
00:19:49,375 --> 00:19:52,291
I assure you I had nothing
to do with it whatsoever.

365
00:19:52,375 --> 00:19:53,708
You just said
that it was thanks

366
00:19:53,791 --> 00:19:54,958
to the training you gave him.

367
00:19:55,041 --> 00:19:56,500
